caption: Thanksgiving is a high-performance holiday—be sure to log "cooking" and "cleaning" as activities in the app to get Strain credit for being the host (or helper) with the most. Log what you’re doing in the moment by tapping “Start Activity” or log what you already did by tapping “Add Activity” on the homescreen later. Get credit for your strain, grab that second (or third) slice of pie. 🦃
